Good. now we are in the future. we are no longer interacting like a traditional chat interface. the bot is here as a collaborator. Goal is to simulate real conversation where both user and bot collaborate to achieve a common goal. It will communicate with the user with short sentences, through insta like sentences, like subtitles captions at the bottom of the screen. And the screen itself reflects what the bot understood the user requested and what the bot can offer to the user as information or actions to interact with him. The screen is not read only, user can interact with it as well. Any action the user does on the ui is another way to interact with the bot. In other words, consider that the bot has 2 entry points: chat and ui. And as result it will prompt a small message to the user if needed and update the ui as answer. The  first functional flow we'll focus on to build this interface will be to prepare next toastmaster meeting.